room_title: Escape room "A Curiouser Heart" by Epic Team Adventures in Seattle
room_description: During a visit to the Quaice Family Library, you run afoul of the enigmatic Gatekeeper. He’s up to his usual tricks and you find yourself in the whimsical world of the Maze of Games. In your 75-minute journey through the maze rescuing yourselves won’t be enough – someone else needs your help! Can you escape and right a literary wrong before the Gatekeeper decides to make you permanent denizens of the maze?
